Preheat oven 350 degrees F; line 24 muffin tins. Combine the Arrowhead Mills Organic All Purpose Flour, Hain Pure Foods Iodized Sea Salt and Hain Pure Foods Gluten Free Featherweight Baking Powder in a bowl. In the bowl of a mixer, combine the sugar, butter, bananas and eggs until well mixed. Add the dry ingredients and mix until evenly combined; stir in chocolate chips. Spoon batter into prepared muffin liners and bake for 28 minutes. Test with a wooden pick. Muffins are done when wooden pick comes out clean. Let cool in pans for 10 minutes and then turn out onto cooling rack to cool completely